1. *Bivšeg* predsednika Srbije sada nema u javnom životu. (Former president of Serbia is no longer active in public life.)
2. Novinari su intervjuisali *bivšeg* ministra o tome šta misli o trenutnoj političkoj situaciji. (Journalists interviewed the former minister about his opinion on the current political situation.)
3. *Bivši* radnici fabrike su organizovali protest zbog neisplaćenih zarada. (Former workers of the factory organized a protest due to unpaid wages.)
4. Ona je odlučila da ostavi *bivšeg* dečka jer je prevario. (She decided to leave her ex-boyfriend because he cheated.)
5. *Bivša* predsednica udruženja je podnela ostavku nakon skandala sa finansijama. (The former president of the association resigned after a financial scandal.)
6. Sadašnja vlada pokušava da sredi probleme koje je ostavila *bivša* vlada. (The current government is trying to fix the problems left by the former government.)
7. *Bivši* fudbaler je otvorio restoran nakon završetka karijere. (The former football player opened a restaurant after retiring.)
8. Neki ljudi teško se nose sa gubitkom *bivših* kolega na poslu. (Some people have a hard time coping with the loss of their former colleagues at work.)
9. Kandidat za gradonačelnika je bio *bivši* direktor javnog preduzeća. (The candidate for mayor used to be the former director of a public enterprise.)
10. *Bivši* studenti univerziteta su se okupili na proslavi desetogodišnjice mature. (Former university students gathered at the 10-year reunion celebration.)